Package: CSB
Type: Package
Title: Contracted Symmetric Beta Distribution for Unit Data
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: 
    person(
        given = "Yuri A.",
        family = "Iriarte",
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        email = "yuri.iriarte@uantof.cl"
    )
Description: Provides functions for the Contracted Symmetric Beta (CSB)
    distribution, including density, distribution function, random generation,
    raw moments, descriptive measures, parameter estimation by moments and
    maximum likelihood, model comparison, and bootstrap goodness-of-fit
    procedures for data supported on the unit interval.
